# CODEOWNERS — auto-requests review from the QuantEcon admin on every PR.
#
# The admin handle is templated in by `onboarding/new-contractor.py`
# (Phase 3b). Combined with branch protection on `main` (also configured
# by onboarding), this gives a "1 approving review required" gate that
# the contractor-payments workflow respects before allowing merge.
#
# CODEOWNERS triggers regardless of PR author (the github-actions[bot]
# opens submission PRs; the codeowner is requested either way), and is
# delivered as a GitHub review-request notification — a sharper signal
# than an @mention in the PR body, and one that GitHub tracks as state
# until the review is filed.

* @$ADMIN
